api_list.name: Get Profile by ID (Cached)
api_list.description:
Only the most recent data, within a 24-hour window, will be provided.

If the information isn't cached, a query will be sent to the social network, ensuring you receive the most up-to-date data available.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://mister-instagrams-scraper1.p.rapidapi.com/instagram/profile-by-id/1574083"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "mister-instagrams-scraper1.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
